CLAIM NO. 5 – LOSS OF PROFIT (WRONGFUL TERMINATION)
AMOUNT: ₹8.90 CRORE | FACT-FIT: 68% | STATUS: SECONDARY
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Hudson Formula: Contract profit 8% × unexecuted value ₹69.62 Cr × delay factor
TOTAL CLAIM 5: ₹8.90 Crore [SECONDARY — needs independent expert valuation]
