AMOUNT: ₹4.15 CRORE | FACT-FIT: 51% | STATUS: PENDING
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Unforeseen rock strata encountered at Chainage 28+100 to 31+400.
Tender soil report indicated Type-II; actual was Type-IV (hard rock blasting required).
[PENDING — Expert Geological Report must be filed before this claim is pressed]

